{
  "stem": "766.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wasn't interested, but my mother wanted, you know, but--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they would be one-- the younger took the violin also, not because we were musical so interested, but my mother wanted it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was status, probably.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish history, but we didn't pay too much-- and not we, the teacher.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was-- a-- I-- the whole school, the personnel were mostly Bundists.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when I was in school, I didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't brainwash us, they didn't influence us, but the teacher of Jewish history wasn't so much interested we should learn Jewish history, that we should know Jewish literature.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he had two hours a week, so one hour was history, which we didn't pay too much attention, and he didn't demand too much.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the other, he read to us, [NON-ENGLISH] and [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this now, the 'Fiddler on the Roof,' I know from his reading.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And also, the tendency in this school was more not to be too much Jewish in talking and not assimilated.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a Jewish gymnasium, but we were very happy to listen to him and begged him to read during the pause, when we were supposed to eat, the other 10, 15 minutes included in the 45 minutes which was the hour.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And let's say, the 'Fiddler on the Roof,' I know from original, but he read to us, and other things.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this what I know a little  of the Jewish literature.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I know how to read too, but I don't read.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yiddish, original, he read to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything Polish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And German.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was German, and we had Latin and such things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this is as it was, but everything was Polish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a Hebrew class too, but we didn't pay too much attention.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
